## About Sherlock

Sherlock is a smart contract security platform that combines audit competitions with an on-chain coverage product. Audit deliverables are published at https://github.com/sherlock-protocol/sherlock-reports/audits.

## Disclaimer

This audit report is a snapshot of the codebase as of the commit hash specified in scope. Subsequent changes to the codebase are out of scope. No security audit can guarantee the absence of vulnerabilities. Use of this report is governed by Sherlock's standard terms.
